data.title: Central European Time
data.meta_description: Exact time now, time zone, time difference, sunrise/sunset time and key facts for Central European Time (CET).
data.text:
Latest change: Summer time started

Switched to UTC +2 / Central European Summer Time (CEST).

The time was set forward eine Stunde from 02:00 to 03:00 local time.

Next change: Winter time starts

Switching to UTC +1 / Central European Time (CET).

The time will be set back eine Stunde from 03:00 to 02:00 local time.
